  Fix sedding & spiff-up postinst message (#59896)
  Remove --background from init script (#64029)
  Add gamin block

  12 Oct 2004; foser <foser@gentoo.org> fam-2.7.0{-r1}.ebuild :
  Add provide for virtual/fam (#67170)

